metadata.name: Night in Isfahan 1
metadata.description:
The number of people cycling in the city is fascinating. You see people of all ages riding bicycle. This photo is taken on the Khaju bridge. 

Location: Isfahan
Date: May 2022
Camera: Sony A7Riii
